// Synth Waves — formes d'onde
// Démo : (wave:X) change le timbre de l'oscillateur
// sine = doux, triangle = moyen, square = creux, sawtooth = riche

@core
@controls
@alphabet.western:browser

S -> Sine Tri Square Saw

Sine -> C4 E4 G4 C5 (wave:sine, vel:80)
Tri -> C4 E4 G4 C5 (wave:triangle, vel:80)
Square -> C4 E4 G4 C5 (wave:square, vel:60)
Saw -> C4 E4 G4 C5 (wave:sawtooth, vel:60)
